Enum ChartPlotOptions

      com.att.aro.main.ChartPlotOptions
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ChartPlotOptions>
public enum ChartPlotOptions
extends java.lang.Enum<ChartPlotOptions>

The ChartPlotOptions enumeration defines constant values that specify the items of diagnostic information that can be plotted on the Diagnostics Chart. The user selects which of these items to plot on the Diagnostics Chart by marking individual check boxes in the View Options dialog box.
